{"tw": {"2824570": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "星的歸還者", "steam_appid": 2824570, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/8c1321365f25577ad3ed8dbbfeb684e2.poster.avif?t=1775054195\" width=780 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/8c1321365f25577ad3ed8dbbfeb684e2.webm?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/8c1321365f25577ad3ed8dbbfeb684e2.mp4?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>✨故事大綱✨</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巴爾多納原本只是位於郊外的一個小國，但是在一次規模巨大的流星雨之後，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巴爾多納的子民獲得了一股遠超現今常識的力量，人們稱為「星之力」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而自那以後，巴爾多納自稱為「星之使者」，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >組建了軍隊侵略周邊的國家，儼然已經成為這片大陸上最大的帝國。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將化身主角希德，希德正是因為當時家鄉的戰爭而失去了雙親，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >喪失一切後也僅僅只是四處流亡，尋找著殉死之處而已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是神並沒有拋棄你，流落街頭時被一名巴爾多納的貴族女姓偷偷帶回家收養了，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自那以後便隱藏了真正的名字長大，進入了軍隊，等待著復仇的機會。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而這樣的機會就在一個夜晚突然來臨，一道閃光從漆黑的天空中直落劈下，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與此同時你的手上出現了一個微微散發著藍色光芒的手環。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被封印的星淵公主，為了奪回被偷走的星之力，與你達成了合作關係，兩人就此踏上了旅途。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💟遊玩目標💟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家在遊戲中扮演主角希德，進行以故事為驅動的橫向塔防戰略遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >總共有6大區域，可以邂逅不同的女主角， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個區域有各自的特色及關卡內容，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 能將所有見到的小怪與女角色收編成為玩家的可使用塔防角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >培育女主角們不但使她們變得更強，還可以與她們碰撞出愛的火花。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>角色介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&lt;暗戀你的前輩大姊姊~露菲娜&gt;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/5c5029321fcf89386dba3075b2991b59.poster.avif?t=1775054195\" width=700 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/5c5029321fcf89386dba3075b2991b59.webm?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/5c5029321fcf89386dba3075b2991b59.mp4?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&lt;調皮且充滿野性的獸娘~賽赫麥特&gt;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/2a26f722d5b175b45c221a5fc8e79292.poster.avif?t=1775054195\" width=700 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/2a26f722d5b175b45c221a5fc8e79292.webm?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/2a26f722d5b175b45c221a5fc8e79292.mp4?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&lt;失去情感的機械少女~零&gt;</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/ce44a8f53775104a0c97260cfc7c02fc.poster.avif?t=1775054195\" width=700 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/ce44a8f53775104a0c97260cfc7c02fc.web