r wrist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To take back the star power that was stolen from her, the Astral Princess has chosen you as her comrade! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The question is...are you ready for the adventure of a lifetime?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💟Objectives💟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Sid in a story-driven, side-scrolling, tower defense game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are a total of 6 main areas where you can meet different female characters. Each area has its own unique features and levels. Players are free to recruit all the creatures and female characters they encounter, who can then be employed for tower defense.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cultivating relationships with the female characters not only makes them stronger, it also leads to some galactic-level lovemaking.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lophina—Older Girl Who's Crushing on You</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/82c9310d8c2fa2ad4e4dfceeac1da200.poster.avif?t=1775054195\" width=700 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/82c9310d8c2fa2ad4e4dfceeac1da200.webm?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/82c9310d8c2fa2ad4e4dfceeac1da200.mp4?t=1775054195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sekhmet—The Playful, Wild Beast Girl</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2824570/extras/ea681aec12f99d2a13bb5553aec03d82.poster.avif